title: PML-N Saqib Khurshid wins PP-233 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (N) candidate, Muhammad Saqib Khurshid has won the election for Punjab Assembly from PP-233, Vehari-V by securing 54,816 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate, Rai Zahoor Ahmad, who bagged 48,491 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn- out remained 54.36%.
